{"tid":447859,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（希望大家可以睇下）有情緒病既人真係好慘","createTime":"2017-10-25T16:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T13:34:17.000Z","uid":106724,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f867449a8900483896cfe5e97dc6ff8e25c0cc96","tid":447859,"uid":106724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"同身邊既人講自己點樣唔開心<br />\n第一次個個都會叫你睇開d <br />\n但如果個個都睇得開呢個世界就唔會有人跳樓<br />\n點諗野其實自己未必可以控制到<br />\n<br />\n第二，第三次就會開始怪你諗埋一邊，覺得你係自己攞黎，覺得你煩。<br />\n<br />\n最憎人講：開唔開心都係要過日子，不如開心咁過<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 屌你老母，生存係香港可以點撚樣開心？</span></span>"},{"pid":"e107bfabecf0e0feca7c4319a706d979fad64a2d","tid":447859,"uid":53794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:32:11.000Z","msg":"儘管講出不快吧<br />\n事與冀盼有落差 請不必驚怕<br />\n我 仍然會冷靜聆聽<br />\n仍然緊守於身邊 與你進退也共鳴"},{"pid":"f83602c6ba9b22e900b31209b00568ad950c8e34","tid":447859,"uid":7954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e712d40924bba1e0513618ccae971273ab4adbc","tid":447859,"uid":115317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"其實情緒病都係病一種<br />\n同心臟病依d病一樣<br />\n唔係自己可以控制<br />\n話諗得正面就諗到"},{"pid":"d0039bdcce5126550ba6f58288fd0452b6cc4372","tid":447859,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:40:31.000Z","msg":"不要說「我有情緒病」<br />\n試著說「我有弱者病」"},{"pid":"44139bc9ead1e40fa959df51bab0273246212692","tid":447859,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T17:00:11.000Z","msg":"好認同紅字<br />\n好多人有情緒病可以係各種原因<br />\n家庭 朋友 愛情 錢 等等<br />\n但最主要都係因為住係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家都灰到冇希望 過得一日得一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf6d70d31d0b46cce08b88354e829dce09022a0","tid":447859,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy